name: Greedy Vacum
description:
Aliens have invaded your house! They demand $100,000 or they'll destroy the world! As a crypto trader, you know exactly what to do. Click yourself and trade away as you gain more expensive computers and printers to print more money. Call your family to help you before it's too late!

Made in 3 hours for Trijam 208 "Fill the Vacuum".

This game is mobile-friendly but may require double tapping on shop buttons.
